{"body": "If you take a look at https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/6752/files#L0R40 you will see the line, which produces wrong path when cache or concat options are enabled. In this case paths will looks like \"/Absolute/path/to/public/\" + \"/Absolute/path/to/asset/file.ext\" which is wrong. \n\nSo to avoid this behaviour I suggest to ignore :cache and :concat options when sprockets is enabled, because sprockets already does things like these options.", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/6520948", "created_at": "2012-06-23T00:12:06Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/6834#issuecomment-6520948", "updated_at": "2012-06-23T00:12:06Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 6834, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/0x000000/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/0x000000/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/0x000000/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/0x000000", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/0x000000/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/0x000000", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/0x000000/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://2.gravatar.com/avatar/5cfb39bb33ec98fae943b5bfcb90b389?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F15f675dcd8b9535eb0954676c0665b74.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/0x000000/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/0x000000/received_events", "gravatar_id": "5cfb39bb33ec98fae943b5bfcb90b389", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/0x000000/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "0x000000", "type": "User", "id": 100340, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/0x000000/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "523803afbd3543c15100c480"}, "id": 6520948, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/6834"}
